Health Metrics gives a complete overview of the product's core functions. 

Using HEART Framework to measure health of a product. 

Happiness --> How satisfied and happy your users are ? (Survey Score)
Engagement --> how users are enagaged on product ? ( Active Users: # of clicks per D/W/D/Q/Y)
Activation --> how users sign-up? (SignUp rate)
Retention --> how long the users stay active ? (DAU, MAU)
Task Success --> How long does it take for a user to complete a task ?(Completion Time)
